        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nI don't think ccsdk/apps/docs is mapped to anything in readthedocs.  I believe all CCSK readthedocs documentation is linked to ccsdk/distributiion/docs - so you probably want to the apps sections there.\n\nRich - is that correct, or is there a mapping I'm perhaps not aware of?",
